text.tspan: Male to female ratio of suicide rates
Gender ratio of suicides per 100,000 people per year. Values higher than 1 indicate countries where more men die
Note: Suicide rates are adjusted for the changing age structure of the population. This chart shows a ratio and does not depict the overall number
or frequency of suicides in a country.
